Package: pluviometer
Title: Precipitation Readings From a Home-made Pluviometer
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(person("Marco", "Bascietto", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "marco@bascietto.name"))
Description: R package to aid in the estimation of precipitation amounts from a home-made
    pluviometer. Building a pluviometer is super-easy, just place a funnel ontop of a cointainer, note funnel diameter and, periodically note the volume of water in the container. 
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    knitr,
    testthat,
    lubridate,
    magrittr,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    ggplot2
Imports:
    assertthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
